Usage

  Add the following to your <<<pom.xml>>>:

+--
[...]
<build>
  [...]
  <plugins>
    [...]
    <plugin>
      <artifactId>org.requs</artifactId>
      <groupId>requs-maven-plugin</groupId>
      <version>${project.version}</version>
    </plugin>
  </plugins>
</build>
+--

  Running <<<mvn requs:compile>>> will create a summary report
  <<<requs.xml>>> in <<<${sign}{project.build.directory}>>>.

  Add the following to your <<<pom.xml>>> (Maven 3.0+):

+--
[...]
<build>
  [...]
  <plugins>
    [...]
    <plugin>
      <artifactId>maven-site-plugin</artifactId>
      <configuration>
        <reportPlugins combine.children="append">
          <plugin>
            <groupId>org.requs</groupId>
            <artifactId>requs-maven-plugin</artifactId>
            <version>${project.version}</version>
          </plugin>
        </reportPlugins>
      </configuration>
    </plugin>
  </plugins>
</build>
+--

  Running <<<mvn site>>> will create a summary report
  in <<<target/site>>>.

